y\naxisymmetric potential. In a companion paper (Hamilton & Rafikov 2019b) we\nprovide a detailed exploration of the resulting orbital dynamics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Feb 2019 18:08:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 18 Feb 2019 10:24:08 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 10 Jun 2019 17:21:11 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 16 Aug 2019 10:39:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-19"}
