 taken by a fixed camera over the\ncourse of one year. Qualitative and quantitative comparison against several\nstate-of-the-art methods on both synthetic and real world images demonstrate\nthat our approach is effective and performs favorably for recovering a clear\nimage from a foggy image.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Feb 2019 18:43:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-05"}
